title: Radius Agents - MediationZone Documentation 9.3 - InfoZone
text: This section describes the Radius Server and Radius Client agents. These are collection and processing agents for real-time workflow configurations. Prerequisites The reader of this information should be familiar with: RADIUS (RFC 2865, http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2865.txt ) RADIUS Accounting (RFC 2866, http://www.ietf.org/rfc/rfc2866.txt ) This section includes the following subsections: Radius Server Agent Radius Client Agent Radius Related UDR Types A Radius Example
